Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.86,0:02:14.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是安閒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.74,0:02:18.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  一點沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.15,0:02:24.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  如果每天天氣都是那麼好的話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.71,0:02:27.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人就會變得越來越懶了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.99,0:02:30.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近一段時間  我老婆她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.92,0:02:32.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天天睡懶覺
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.01,0:02:35.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連早飯都不做了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.81,0:02:39.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂「春眠不覺曉」嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.89,0:02:43.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且她最近健忘得厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.98,0:02:47.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有次把孩子都忘在街上了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.83,0:02:48.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺嚴重的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.84,0:02:52.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望別等你回家的時候都不認識你了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.58,0:02:57.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  沒到這步真是謝天謝地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.74,0:03:04.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你妻子  晚上不會睡不著吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.64,0:03:08.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？睡得挺好啊  呼嚕聲可大了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.57,0:03:09.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.20,0:03:14.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好什麼啊  吵得我都睡不著了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.07,0:03:16.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這兒有治打鼾的藥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.05,0:03:18.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個管用嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.82,0:03:24.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.63,0:03:29.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  剛才你們說的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.35,0:03:32.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？治打鼾的藥嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.51,0:03:36.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  是關於健忘的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.85,0:03:39.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果晚上睡不好的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.15,0:03:41.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很糟糕嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.72,0:03:45.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想到什麼了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.87,0:03:50.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.55,0:03:55.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.30,0:03:57.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快幫幫我  加持
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.85,0:03:59.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家裡有個奇怪的動物…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.10,0:04:01.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪的動物？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.15,0:04:06.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是說螃蟹？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.88,0:04:08.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個你都忘記了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.56,0:04:12.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每年到這個時節都會上岸產卵的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.22,0:04:15.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.72,0:04:20.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是加持的朋友嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.70,0:04:21.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.10,0:04:23.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是我剛認識的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.94,0:04:25.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蟲師銀古先生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.53,0:04:27.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蟲師？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.27,0:04:30.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以稍微打擾一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.61,0:04:36.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請便  我是加持的母親  小夜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.59,0:04:40.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都是這種狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.32,0:04:44.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前可是位很穩重的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.91,0:04:47.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說有時也會忘事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.89,0:04:49.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是從去年春天起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.97,0:04:52.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就健忘得奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.48,0:04:56.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一天  因為難得來了很多客人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.95,0:04:59.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我特別買了媽媽喜歡的烤丸子回來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.53,0:05:02.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個點心真好吃！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.16,0:05:05.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽還是第一次吃到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.79,0:05:10.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼啊  以前不是也偶爾會吃嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.06,0:05:15.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有啊  是不是你自己偷偷吃過？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.68,0:05:21.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽關於烤丸子的記憶全都消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.57,0:05:24.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有一次
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.14,0:05:27.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不常穿的衣服還是賣掉算了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.01,0:05:31.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.83,0:05:34.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有這樣的衣服嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.42,0:05:36.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是因為這件很貴所以一直捨不得穿嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.51,0:05:38.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.61,0:05:43.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  也有這種的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.16,0:05:47.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為會把臉色襯得難看  所以不常穿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.12,0:05:49.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不常穿的衣服中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.37,0:05:53.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎把所有帶圖案的衣服都忘記了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.45,0:05:56.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天真冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.12,0:06:03.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真…真嚇人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.96,0:06:05.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要做這麼奇怪的事情啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.28,0:06:10.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪？只是打了個噴嚏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.21,0:06:12.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噴嚏？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.18,0:06:15.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她連打噴嚏都不記得了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.93,0:06:19.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有就是過年去親戚家拜年的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.59,0:06:24.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加持  對面的兩個人是誰來著？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.20,0:06:26.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿真伯父和阿滿伯母
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.41,0:06:29.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  他們邊上的人呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.35,0:06:32.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是你妹妹呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.29,0:06:34.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連妹妹都…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.28,0:06:37.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確  很奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.40,0:06:42.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與其說是健忘  不如說是階段性的喪失記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.76,0:06:43.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.24,0:06:49.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且現在她不論白天晚上都不睡覺  一直在工作
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.08,0:06:55.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前還能看見她做家事休息時在庭院的樹下午睡的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.61,0:06:58.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定有哪裡不對勁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.98,0:07:02.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚飯做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.89,0:07:04.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,銀古先生也一起吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.67,0:07:06.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然也沒什麼好東西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.26,0:07:08.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加持
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.36,0:07:11.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一會兒你想一想你母親忘記了哪些東西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.24,0:07:14.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能想到多少都儘量寫下來給我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.89,0:07:22.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.22,0:07:25.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  請別介意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.55,0:07:29.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是給出門旅行的丈夫做的蔭膳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.55,0:07:29.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fs28}（蔭膳：家人為了起到外出旅行的人平安而供奉的食物）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.31,0:07:31.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蔭膳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.08,0:07:36.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  他是一年到頭都四處奔波的行腳商人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.34,0:07:41.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳說這樣在外面就不會缺食少餐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.58,0:07:44.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實也就是表示個心意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.51,0:07:48.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不會是連丈夫死了都給忘了吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.63,0:07:50.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開始吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.26,0:07:53.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太浪費了  我都說過不讓你這麼做了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.70,0:07:55.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又用不了多少米
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.79,0:07:58.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這樣媽媽吃的就會少了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.75,0:08:02.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以為你爸在外奔波是為了誰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.23,0:08:06.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他可比在家裡的我要餓多了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.96,0:08:10.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是又賺不到幾個錢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.14,0:08:13.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在附近工作不好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.16,0:08:16.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加持
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.95,0:08:19.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平時已經到了該回來的時節了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.89,0:08:21.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連個消息都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.20,0:08:26.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽變得這麼迷糊都是因為總是在擔心爸爸他…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.02,0:08:28.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要說了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.86,0:08:31.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加持！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.21,0:08:36.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃完飯扔下碗就跑…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.09,0:08:39.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.81,0:08:43.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子也希望爸爸在身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.56,0:08:49.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我丈夫除了溫柔就是沒什麼長處的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.81,0:08:52.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在一定在哪裡迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.82,0:08:57.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他擔心的不只是他父親吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.32,0:09:02.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.20,0:09:07.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是被那孩子請來的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.64,0:09:10.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  已經大致上聽過你的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.65,0:09:14.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  你知道什麼了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.20,0:09:17.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前還什麼都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.60,0:09:20.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.63,0:09:25.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了那孩子  當然也是為了我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.66,0:09:28.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.39,0:09:33.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我害怕  再這樣下去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.17,0:09:36.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定哪天連孩子他爸和孩子都忘記了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.13,0:09:42.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並且忘記自己忘記了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.65,0:09:48.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再沒有比這更可怕的了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.10,0:09:50.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寫完了麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.04,0:09:52.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  大致寫完了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.04,0:09:56.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.42,0:10:03.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得她忘記東西應該有一定規律
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.01,0:10:06.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在差了點什麼  還是搞不明白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.02,0:10:17.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  忘記的親戚裡面有沒有什麼共同點？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.67,0:10:23.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  大家都是住在河對面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.72,0:10:25.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平常很少碰面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.74,0:10:31.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？只是從日常生活中接觸少的東西開始忘記？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.80,0:10:35.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對  如果是這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.42,0:10:37.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她應該早就把丈夫的事情忘記了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.18,0:10:51.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼晚了  也完全沒有要睡覺的意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.20,0:10:52.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.48,0:10:56.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽她說即使想睡也睡不著
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.93,0:11:01.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  每天晚上都像這樣坐在織布機前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.33,0:11:05.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說是為了怕忘記父親而反覆想著以前的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.08,0:11:10.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.22,0:11:16.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是能睡著  等待就不那麼難熬了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.72,0:11:22.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暖風
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.28,0:11:24.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花香
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.60,0:11:27.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,織布聲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.96,0:11:33.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這樣的深夜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.59,0:11:34.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若在平常
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.42,0:11:42.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是為令人落入深沉的睡眠中而存在的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.53,0:11:54.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.03,0:11:56.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總算是開始犯睏了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.54,0:12:05.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就醒了	
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.92,0:12:08.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經是早上了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.19,0:12:13.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做飯  做飯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.59,0:12:17.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.09,0:12:33.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  果然是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.26,0:12:38.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吞噬記憶的蟲？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.79,0:12:41.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  叫作「影魂」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.58,0:12:44.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體呈半透明的黑色幕狀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.25,0:12:47.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡潛藏在古樹的下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.73,0:12:48.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裝作是陰影
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.70,0:12:53.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等有人或動物在樹下休息的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.56,0:12:56.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦睡著  它就會從耳朵裡鑽入腦中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.41,0:13:00.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿主就會變得幾乎無法睡眠
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.54,0:13:04.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且漸漸的開始喪失記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.08,0:13:10.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在庭院裡的櫻樹下面有這個…？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.06,0:13:11.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有可能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.88,0:13:17.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等吞噬了宿主一定量的記憶後  就在體內分裂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.08,0:13:21.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分身就趁宿主打盹的時候跑到外面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.19,0:13:25.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續潛伏在樹蔭中  如此繁衍不息
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.74,0:13:31.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它們本來是害怕陽光照射的脆弱生物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.05,0:13:36.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  一旦鑽入生物體內就會潛伏在腦中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.15,0:13:38.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這時就沒有辦法對付它們了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.33,0:13:41.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是說治不好了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.07,0:13:46.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前所知的影魂的弱點只有陽光
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.78,0:13:49.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不能打開頭腦照射陽光…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.33,0:13:56.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  也許有辦法阻止不想忘記的事情被忘掉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.17,0:14:00.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打個比方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.77,0:14:04.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人的記憶就像是放在一個大櫃子裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.74,0:14:07.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烤丸子的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.42,0:14:10.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住得遠的親戚的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.67,0:14:11.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打噴嚏的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.49,0:14:16.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些都分門別類地放在不同的抽屜裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.18,0:14:20.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,影魂會一個一個抽出抽屜吃掉它
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.36,0:14:24.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吞吃的順序和你重視的程度之類沒有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.08,0:14:26.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以說是無序的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.83,0:14:33.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  有些記憶影魂不會吞噬
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.70,0:14:40.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是你每天都會做  會見到  會想的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.54,0:14:42.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如做飯的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.08,0:14:44.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,織布的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.11,0:14:46.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兒子的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.32,0:14:51.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有在記憶中見到的丈夫的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.99,0:14:54.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許影魂是為了保障宿主的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.06,0:15:00.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不會吞噬這些涉及日常生活的記憶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.82,0:15:05.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  這樣的事情都不會忘記？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.57,0:15:08.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這只是我的推測
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.76,0:15:12.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  如果之前記憶是從底層開始被吞噬的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.25,0:15:17.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許什麼時候那些也會被吞噬掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.55,0:15:20.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  我能想到的方法就是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.45,0:15:23.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儘量多儲存記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.89,0:15:28.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並且不斷地回想不願意忘記的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.29,0:15:35.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了  我會試試的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.59,0:15:36.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊  媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.05,0:15:40.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也不要總是待在家裡  出去走走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.80,0:15:44.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  是該如此
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.78,0:15:48.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們別等了  去找你爸爸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.24,0:15:49.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.26,0:15:51.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛  一副傻樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.56,0:15:56.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很久以前就想這麼做了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.35,0:16:02.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  又害怕得知你爸爸出了什麼事…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.83,0:16:05.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  我已經等夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.18,0:16:07.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是怎麼找啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.79,0:16:11.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你父親以前經常提起西邊的小鎮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.85,0:16:14.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼先試著從那裡找起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.96,0:16:16.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.86,0:16:20.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會和我一起去吧  加持
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.58,0:16:26.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就在這裡分別吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.05,0:16:27.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.70,0:16:33.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這幾天給你添麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.22,0:16:36.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.21,0:16:38.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.23,0:16:41.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  請多保重
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.77,0:16:46.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個決定對那兩個人來說真的好嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.58,0:16:53.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道他們旅行結果的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.04,0:16:56.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經過去了一年
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.14,0:17:03.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲  已經回來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.27,0:17:06.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,銀古先生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.11,0:17:08.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.86,0:17:10.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您想要點什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.67,0:17:15.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你母親很有精神嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.75,0:17:16.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.10,0:17:18.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇見你父親了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.14,0:17:20.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.93,0:17:23.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就在西邊的小鎮上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.89,0:17:27.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那裡的另外一個家生活著
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.37,0:17:30.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.86,0:17:33.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去那戶人家看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.94,0:17:44.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.04,0:17:46.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  舒服嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.97,0:17:54.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽  為什麼一句話不說就走了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.82,0:17:58.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.05,0:18:06.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家的路上  媽媽一直沉默不語
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.49,0:18:10.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不吃不睡的  終於…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.66,0:18:14.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽？稍微…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.06,0:18:18.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽！媽媽！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.82,0:18:30.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是很累吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.38,0:18:36.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽倒下之後一連睡了好幾天
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.66,0:18:57.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上了啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.99,0:19:24.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才  好像有什麼東西出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.91,0:19:30.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.64,0:19:33.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？這種表情？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.97,0:19:44.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡得真香
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.09,0:19:47.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  該做飯了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.19,0:19:51.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.23,0:19:53.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.24,0:19:58.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們為什麼會在這裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.12,0:20:04.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們去山上玩  正在往回走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.78,0:20:06.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.91,0:20:11.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才是什麼聲音？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.92,0:20:15.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的啦  吃點什麼東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.63,0:20:18.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得是  肚子都餓扁了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.16,0:20:32.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊…快點…快點…回家吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.15,0:20:35.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天早晨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.77,0:20:38.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽把除了我的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.26,0:20:40.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家裡的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.93,0:20:42.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有身邊的事情以外的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.80,0:20:48.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有事情全都忘記了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.37,0:20:54.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在她失落的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.54,0:20:57.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記憶的大半都被吞噬了嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.46,0:21:07.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  她照樣沒有忘記做飯的方法和我的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.84,0:21:09.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是因為我們按照銀古先生說的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.70,0:21:13.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天到外面去接觸各種各樣的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.85,0:21:17.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然母親還是會在第二天忘記大部分事情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.64,0:21:21.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是她每天都很快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.94,0:21:25.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在還是幾乎不睡覺嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.04,0:21:30.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  還是和以前一樣徹夜織布
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.49,0:21:34.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  還是和以前一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.10,0:21:39.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  和以前完全一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.48,0:21:44.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.27,0:21:46.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.93,0:21:49.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飯已經做好了  快去洗手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.89,0:21:50.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.06,0:21:59.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽  你又多盛了一碗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.63,0:22:01.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.23,0:22:05.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊…明明只要盛你和我的就夠了…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.02,0:22:11.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底…為什麼會覺得必須要這麼做呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.54,0:22:18.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  這樣做的時候會有種安心的感覺呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.87,0:22:21.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是為什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.96,0:22:25.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟是怎麼回事呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.99,0:23:37.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1500,0)}迷繭探虛


